# Testing Instance Info di Local Environment

Untuk test info instance di local environment, Anda bisa set environment variables di .env:

```env
# Instance Information (untuk testing di local)
INSTANCE_NAME="Web-Server-Development-12345678"
AWS_INSTANCE_ID="i-1234567890abcdef0"
AWS_AVAILABILITY_ZONE="us-east-1a"
AWS_INSTANCE_TYPE="t3.micro"
```

Atau buat file `.env.local` untuk testing:

```env
APP_NAME="Laravel Instance Monitor"
APP_ENV=local
APP_KEY=base64:your-app-key-here
APP_DEBUG=true
APP_TIMEZONE=UTC
APP_URL=http://localhost

# Instance Info untuk testing
INSTANCE_NAME="Test-Server-Local-Dev"
AWS_INSTANCE_ID="i-test12345"
AWS_AVAILABILITY_ZONE="local-zone-1a"
AWS_INSTANCE_TYPE="development"

# Database
DB_CONNECTION=sqlite
DB_DATABASE=database/database.sqlite

CACHE_STORE=file
FILESYSTEM_DISK=local
QUEUE_CONNECTION=database
SESSION_DRIVER=file
SESSION_LIFETIME=120

VITE_APP_NAME="${APP_NAME}"
```

## Untuk Production di AWS

Di AWS, info akan otomatis terdeteksi dari metadata service:
- Instance ID dari `http://169.254.169.254/latest/meta-data/instance-id`
- Instance Type dari `http://169.254.169.254/latest/meta-data/instance-type`
- Availability Zone dari `http://169.254.169.254/latest/meta-data/placement/availability-zone`
- IP addresses dari metadata service

User data script akan otomatis set INSTANCE_NAME dengan format:
`Web-Server-{AZ}-{SHORT_INSTANCE_ID}`

Contoh: `Web-Server-us-east-1a-12345678`